channel.title: Project Insanity Remake (Had to quit) (Fixed Lunars)
channel.description:
[size=14pt]Well me and my friend Sam were wanted to have a server to play & pk on & shit. So I decided since I'm decent with PI's we should play on an oldschool PI for fun... But I recently found out that in 2 days I'm going to be going somewhere for a little under a month, so I'm just going to release this.[/size]
[size=12pt]What I've done: Followed a bunch of tuts... ... I barely did anything myself, used a tutorial for almost everything. But I did add a donator shop myself :D not really worth mentioning though. So what was done: Lunars Completely Fixed (to my knowledge) Some commands shaped & turned around... Was probably given about 5 or so warnings in eclipse. L[/size]
[URL=http://imageshack.us/photo/my-images/821/fixedlunars.png/][IMG]http://img821.imageshack.us/img821/3800/fixedlunars.png[/img][/URL]
I originally used 'Project Insanity - Normal PI - All Dupes fixed.' From 'Jack' on RLocus. Creds: Sanity Jinrake- rlocus Robgob69- rlocus Jake- rlocus Me- .25% :)
Here's the download link. If any of you have any questions or need help setting it up, I'll be online for 2 more days, so go ahead and reply to this topic [URL=http://up.ht/MIPk1t]ProjectInsanityRemake.zip - 28.7 MB[/URL]
